    <item>
      <title>南非铁路、电力改造的关键在于杜绝电缆盗窃</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/south-africa-rail-power-revamp-hinges-on-ending-cable-theft</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非两家最大的国有企业多年来深陷腐败和盗窃的泥潭，它们的复苏依赖于一个共同的要素：保护数千英里的电缆免遭盗窃，并铺设更多的电缆。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/south-africa-rail-power-revamp-hinges-on-ending-cable-theft</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 09:33:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
